			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-2094809">
									

<p>An alternative is that the difference between a god and a reality bender is that the former doesn't actually give off humes - it is part of base reality. An RB is something that has godlike powers but shouldn't.</p>
<p>Or that exceptionally powerful RBs are indiscernible from gods.</p>
<p>Though gotta shake my head at making 343 powerful in this. i know it's the go to example, but it's still lame.</p>

